    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-06-19T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-06-19T14:00:00-05:00" n="810"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d810">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/10369</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_GWE1"
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-06-19T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 19, 1918, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your June 14, noon. Inform Department immediately by cable if the seven points
                    set forth in your June 14 were agreed to and are to be immediately acted upon by
                    the Cuban Government.<note n="2" xml:id="d810fn2">Answered June 19, “Yes.” (File
                        No. 763.72/10417.)</note>
                </p>
                <pb facs="0904" n="1738" xml:id="pg_1738"/>
                <p>You may inform that Government that coal sent to Cuba is “for the benefit of
                    Cuba”.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
